\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 Because the mechanisms of action of various zinc transients are still unknown,
 our contemplation on the subject is purely hypothetical, nevertheless,
 we can deduce that 
\emph on
terra incognita
\emph default
 of Zn(II) fluctuations and the interdependence of 
\begin_inset ERT
